WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:51.380
Tsuru Returns the Favor

3
00:01:47.340 --> 00:01:49.380
It's time you cut your visit short.

4
00:01:49.380 --> 00:01:53.890
Don't you know who pulls
the strings in this country?

5
00:01:53.890 --> 00:01:55.350
No idea!

6
00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:57.060
It's Kaido, right?!

7
00:01:57.430 --> 00:01:58.430
We're here to...

8
00:02:00.060 --> 00:02:01.930
take down an Emperor!

9
00:02:01.930 --> 00:02:03.390
Hey, Luffy!

10
00:02:03.390 --> 00:02:06.900
Kin'emon said we shouldn't
say things like that, either!

11
00:02:06.900 --> 00:02:07.610
Wha...?

12
00:02:09.280 --> 00:02:10.530
That was a lie!

13
00:02:10.860 --> 00:02:12.070
I don't know who!

14
00:02:19.950 --> 00:02:24.330
The probability of you two
surviving the month...

15
00:02:29.250 --> 00:02:31.590
is 19 percent.

16
00:02:33.800 --> 00:02:37.300
By the way, where'd you get that sword?

17
00:02:39.220 --> 00:02:41.310
Some named blade, thus and verily.

18
00:02:45.650 --> 00:02:49.190
Yeah, I'm certain it's a named blade.

19
00:02:49.190 --> 00:02:50.650
Let me see it for a sec.

20
00:02:54.360 --> 00:02:55.070
No way!

21
00:02:55.070 --> 00:02:58.450
You can't use a sword anyway
so just give it to me!

22
00:02:59.450 --> 00:03:00.950
I'll cut them up, verily!

23
00:03:01.450 --> 00:03:02.250
Charge.

24
00:03:08.580 --> 00:03:10.800
This is a sword fight, verily!

25
00:03:11.880 --> 00:03:14.130
Don't throw the scabbard!

26
00:03:18.850 --> 00:03:21.140
Gum-Gum...

27
00:03:21.680 --> 00:03:22.720
Pistol!

28
00:03:23.850 --> 00:03:26.810
It's not a damn pistol!

29
00:03:30.150 --> 00:03:32.110
Even the lizard's after me!

30
00:03:34.360 --> 00:03:35.570
Damn you!

31
00:03:44.410 --> 00:03:45.910
Straw Sword.

32
00:04:09.190 --> 00:04:11.150
What kind of sword is that?!

33
00:04:11.610 --> 00:04:13.570
That poor lizard!

34
00:04:24.870 --> 00:04:26.120
That was fast!

35
00:04:55.320 --> 00:04:56.690
Impressive.

36
00:04:57.150 --> 00:04:58.650
What just happened?!

37
00:05:24.260 --> 00:05:26.850
Minus One Life.

38
00:05:33.810 --> 00:05:39.070
These strawmen represent my subordinates.

39
00:05:44.780 --> 00:05:49.290
I can store them in my body
with my Straw-Straw power...

40
00:05:49.290 --> 00:05:51.160
so I won't be harmed.

41
00:05:52.040 --> 00:05:55.250
If I store ten of them, I can die ten times.

42
00:06:10.680 --> 00:06:14.150
Now, let's play a game.

43
00:06:16.150 --> 00:06:17.110
A game?!

44
00:06:20.400 --> 00:06:21.780
That's right...

45
00:06:22.280 --> 00:06:24.950
With this Strawman's Card!

46
00:07:27.680 --> 00:07:34.390
I'm not so honorable that I'd face two of
the Worst Generation on equal footing.

47
00:07:34.390 --> 00:07:37.140
He's a bigger pain in the ass than I thought...

48
00:07:38.900 --> 00:07:40.520
but I should've figured!

49
00:07:48.990 --> 00:07:50.450
Let's begin.

50
00:08:04.460 --> 00:08:06.760
The Reversed Fool!

51
00:08:08.220 --> 00:08:11.600
Damn, this signifies internal discord.

52
00:08:31.820 --> 00:08:35.410
Sorry, I'll draw a better card next time.

53
00:08:35.750 --> 00:08:43.090
I must accept the risks because
some cards can push me beyond my limits.

54
00:08:58.890 --> 00:09:01.730
Hey! What are you doing, boy?!

55
00:09:03.560 --> 00:09:04.520
Hawkins!

56
00:09:05.440 --> 00:09:06.730
Fear not.

57
00:09:10.740 --> 00:09:13.200
Tama! Stay with us, Tama!

58
00:09:13.870 --> 00:09:15.490
She's burning up!

59
00:09:15.490 --> 00:09:18.370
That's must be why the dog's in a hurry.

60
00:09:23.000 --> 00:09:24.340
You bastards!

61
00:09:24.340 --> 00:09:26.090
We won't let you escape!

62
00:09:26.630 --> 00:09:28.880
Hawkins! They're getting away!

63
00:09:33.590 --> 00:09:35.430
I drew a good card.

64
00:09:38.470 --> 00:09:41.230
The Reversed Hierophant.

65
00:09:42.980 --> 00:09:44.980
The card of pursuit!

66
00:10:14.050 --> 00:10:16.100
Hey, Luffy!

67
00:10:16.100 --> 00:10:17.680
Protect the kid!

68
00:10:20.890 --> 00:10:22.390
I'll...

69
00:10:27.480 --> 00:10:28.980
handle...

70
00:10:30.610 --> 00:10:31.530
this!

71
00:10:54.930 --> 00:10:57.050
You're actually pretty tough.

72
00:11:08.770 --> 00:11:09.820
Nails?!

73
00:12:03.620 --> 00:12:05.250
Two-Sword Style...

74
00:12:08.170 --> 00:12:09.710
Nigiri...

75
00:12:12.670 --> 00:12:14.460
Toro...

76
00:12:16.170 --> 00:12:17.720
Samon!

77
00:12:45.700 --> 00:12:48.290
Should we go after them, Hawkins?!

78
00:13:00.970 --> 00:13:02.220
The Hierophant.

79
00:13:03.890 --> 00:13:05.930
It's the card of assistance.

80
00:13:05.930 --> 00:13:10.060
Someone will lead them away to safety...

81
00:13:12.900 --> 00:13:15.320
What an annoying guy...

82
00:13:16.940 --> 00:13:20.070
So, how's the kid doing?

83
00:13:24.490 --> 00:13:25.410
So warm!

84
00:13:25.950 --> 00:13:27.660
Her temperature keeps rising.

85
00:13:27.660 --> 00:13:28.500
Dog!

86
00:13:28.500 --> 00:13:29.790
Run faster!

87
00:13:56.940 --> 00:13:58.730
Huh? What's the problem?

88
00:14:04.660 --> 00:14:06.830
Wait... are you...?

89
00:14:06.830 --> 00:14:08.370
Are you lost?!

90
00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:14.380
We've got no time to waste...

91
00:14:14.960 --> 00:14:16.130
Let's just...

92
00:14:16.880 --> 00:14:18.500
go right.

93
00:14:19.050 --> 00:14:20.510
You should go left.

94
00:14:23.010 --> 00:14:26.600
You samurai are so strong.

95
00:14:27.930 --> 00:14:29.430
Who are you?!

96
00:14:31.390 --> 00:14:34.440
I can't believe you repelled Hawkins.

97
00:14:36.020 --> 00:14:36.940
You're...

98
00:14:37.690 --> 00:14:42.740
I'm the one you saved earlier,
green gentleman.

99
00:14:48.580 --> 00:14:50.490
My name is Tsuru.

100
00:14:50.870 --> 00:14:55.790
Otsuru

Teahouse
Owner

101
00:14:58.290 --> 00:15:02.210
Were you... hiding in his tail all this time?!

102
00:15:04.090 --> 00:15:05.300
Yes!

103
00:15:06.760 --> 00:15:09.390
Thank you for saving me.

104
00:15:13.680 --> 00:15:14.810
Here!

105
00:15:14.810 --> 00:15:18.690
Could you at least wipe the sweat off of her?

106
00:15:18.690 --> 00:15:20.820
Oh! Thanks!

107
00:15:21.900 --> 00:15:24.400
I hope this doesn't sound too presumptuous...

108
00:15:24.400 --> 00:15:29.160
but would you allow me
to care for young Otama?

109
00:15:29.160 --> 00:15:30.660
You know her?

110
00:15:30.660 --> 00:15:31.410
Yes.

111
00:15:32.450 --> 00:15:33.700
I see!

112
00:15:33.700 --> 00:15:34.830
Please do!

113
00:15:35.460 --> 00:15:40.420
She drank the polluted river water
because she was so hungry.

114
00:15:41.420 --> 00:15:43.710
Instead of searching for a doctor...

115
00:15:44.590 --> 00:15:46.590
please bring her to my teahouse.

116
00:15:46.590 --> 00:15:47.720
Tea?!

117
00:15:48.390 --> 00:15:50.510
This is no time for tea!

118
00:15:50.930 --> 00:15:53.020
If we don't hurry up, she's gonna die!

119
00:15:55.180 --> 00:15:59.980
I don't know this kid, so it might
not be any of my business but...

120
00:16:01.020 --> 00:16:01.650
No, no...

121
00:16:02.520 --> 00:16:07.860
We have a medical herb that is
effective against the river's poison.

122
00:16:07.860 --> 00:16:12.530
That'll be the best way
to treat Otama's condition.

123
00:16:16.660 --> 00:16:17.920
I see.

124
00:16:17.920 --> 00:16:19.540
Then please, help us!

125
00:16:20.250 --> 00:16:21.630
Thank you!

126
00:16:22.710 --> 00:16:25.260
To return the favor I owe you...

127
00:16:25.260 --> 00:16:28.720
let me treat you, too, green gentleman...

128
00:16:43.980 --> 00:16:44.020
Okobore Town
Kuri
Wano

129
00:16:44.020 --> 00:16:44.070
Okobore Town
Kuri
Wano

130
00:16:44.070 --> 00:16:44.110
Okobore Town
Kuri
Wano

131
00:16:44.110 --> 00:16:44.150
Okobore Town
Kuri
Wano

132
00:16:44.150 --> 00:16:49.400
Okobore Town
Kuri
Wano

133
00:16:51.620 --> 00:16:52.870
Here you go.

134
00:16:54.790 --> 00:16:58.410
The teahouse's dumplings are a rare treat.

135
00:16:59.750 --> 00:17:02.250
They're the only things...

136
00:17:03.130 --> 00:17:05.500
that keep me going.

137
00:17:09.220 --> 00:17:10.800
You exaggerate...

138
00:17:11.180 --> 00:17:15.310
Soon, you'll be able to eat as many
as you want just like you used to.

139
00:17:17.140 --> 00:17:19.270
I hope so...

140
00:17:19.690 --> 00:17:24.610
Okiku

Teahouse
Waitress

141
00:17:26.480 --> 00:17:29.820
Hey, old man, the place is closing now!

142
00:17:30.150 --> 00:17:31.820
Get lost!

143
00:17:35.990 --> 00:17:38.790
Now, Okiku.

144
00:17:39.120 --> 00:17:42.080
You can't pay the street tax, right?

145
00:17:42.080 --> 00:17:44.920
All I'm saying is that I'll help you.

146
00:17:45.500 --> 00:17:48.380
If you become my wife...

147
00:17:48.380 --> 00:17:50.090
you won't have to work!

148
00:17:50.840 --> 00:17:56.350
Every day, you'd be able to eat as much
delicious food from the farm as you want!

149
00:17:59.020 --> 00:18:01.310
Our social standings are too different.

150
00:18:01.850 --> 00:18:04.060
If you're not ordering anything, would you please...

151
00:18:04.770 --> 00:18:06.320
take your leave?

152
00:18:06.320 --> 00:18:09.280
I don't wanna eat anything from this place!

153
00:18:09.780 --> 00:18:13.950
The dumplings and tea are made
from others' leftovers!

154
00:18:14.700 --> 00:18:19.660
Say, you do know who I am, right?

155
00:18:20.540 --> 00:18:24.420
I'm a famous yokozuna from the capital.

156
00:18:30.420 --> 00:18:33.590
I'm the best sumo wrestler in Wano,

157
00:18:33.930 --> 00:18:38.220
Urashima!

158
00:18:38.930 --> 00:18:41.810
It's time you quit this seedy teahouse!

159
00:18:41.810 --> 00:18:48.360
You need to stop living off of
someone's leftovers, so that you and I...

160
00:18:48.360 --> 00:18:51.360
so that we can... y'know...?

161
00:18:51.940 --> 00:18:54.280
Okiku!

162
00:19:01.290 --> 00:19:03.290
Miss Otsuru!

163
00:19:05.540 --> 00:19:08.420
Otama drank poisoned water from the river!

164
00:19:08.420 --> 00:19:10.710
Oh! That's serious!

165
00:19:11.210 --> 00:19:14.220
Please! Do what you can to help her!

166
00:19:14.550 --> 00:19:15.630
Okiku!

167
00:19:16.010 --> 00:19:18.220
Brew the cinquefoil!

168
00:19:18.220 --> 00:19:20.060
Of course, right away!

169
00:19:20.060 --> 00:19:20.680
Hey!

170
00:19:21.970 --> 00:19:24.690
Who are you idiots?!

171
00:19:26.100 --> 00:19:27.270
Hey!

172
00:19:27.270 --> 00:19:28.480
Get out the way.

173
00:19:28.480 --> 00:19:29.560
Huh?!

174
00:19:31.230 --> 00:19:33.570
Why would I have to do that...?!

175
00:19:38.410 --> 00:19:42.620
Okiku! I have a match in Bakura Town later!

176
00:19:43.250 --> 00:19:47.370
If you're interested,
come and see how strong I am!

177
00:19:50.000 --> 00:19:52.750
Atop a Mountain...

178
00:19:55.760 --> 00:19:57.760
It's them, isn't it?!

179
00:19:57.760 --> 00:19:59.510
It's the Straw Hats!

180
00:20:01.680 --> 00:20:04.640
Should I go tell them
before they make any trouble?!

181
00:20:04.980 --> 00:20:06.180
You'd better not!

182
00:20:06.730 --> 00:20:09.600
You'll draw people's attention!

183
00:20:10.110 --> 00:20:14.990
For now, let's just report this to the captain.
